x\left(t\right) = c_1 e^{-\omega_n \left( \zeta + \sqrt{\zeta^2 - 1} \right)t} + c_2 e^{-\omega_n \left( \zeta - \sqrt{\zeta^2 - 1} \right)t}
\end{equation*}\] | | \(\zeta = +1\) | Real & equal roots: exponential, convergent | \[\begin{equation*}
